OL,5,
OL,6,CG1974FPercy Thower appears on Blue
OL,7,FPeter (BBC One) for the first time.
OL,8,
OL,9,CG1987FDebbie Thrower joins the BBC TV
OL,10,Fnews presenting team, and presents
OL,11,FNewsView (BBC Two) for the first time.
OL,12,
OL,13,CG1988FThe BBC announces plans for a
OL,14,Fmajor overhaul of the Nine o'Clock News
OL,15,F(BBC One). The intention is to switch
OL,16,Fback to a single presenter each night
OL,17,Fand to appoint a dedicated team of
OL,18,Freporters and producers.
